info-enter-correct-email = Make sure to enter the correct email address below, no emails will be sent if you enter a wrong email address.
info-resend-login-mail = Resend login email

## emails
login-mail =
    Someone (probably you) has requested a new login link for https://geschenke.oli-obk.de .
    
    Click the following link to login:
    https://geschenke.oli-obk.de/account/login_form_key?key={ $autologin }
    
    Your friendly neighborhood Geschenke-Bot
    
    
    If it was not you, no damage has been done, just use the new login link
    Your account is still perfectly safe
registration-mail =
    Someone (probably you) has created an account for { $email_address } at https://geschenke.oli-obk.de .
    
    Click the following link to login:
    https://geschenke.oli-obk.de/account/login_form_key?key={ $autologin }
    
    Your friendly neighborhood Geschenke-Bot
    
    
    If it was not you, visit
    https://geschenke.oli-obk.de/nuke/{ $autologin }.
    to remove your email address from our database
invite-mail =
    Hi { $name },
    
    { $who } has invited you ({ $email_address }) to see their wishlist at https://geschenke.oli-obk.de .
    
    Click the following link to see the wishlist:
    https://geschenke.oli-obk.de/account/login_form_key?key={ $autologin }&wishlist={$inviter_id}
    
    Your friendly neighborhood Geschenke-Bot
    
    
    If you do not want your email address to be stored in our database, visit
    https://geschenke.oli-obk.de/nuke/{ $autologin }.
    to remove it.

